reviewText: Nice, informative video.  Lot's of places visited and discussed.  If you haven't been to NYC, I recommend this video to give you ideas of where to go!

I'VE ALWAYS BEEN FASCINATED BY THE APPEAL OF "THE BIG APPLE" AND THIS PRESENTATION DID NOT DISAPPOINT MY EXPECTATIONS. IT HAD JUST THE RIGHT AMOUNT OF CONTENT PRESENTED AT EACH STOP ON THIS TOUR OF THE CITY. I'M SURE THAT THERE ARE MORE SPECIFIC OFFERINGS AVAILABLE, BUT FOR MY PURPOSE, THIS WAS WELL WORTH IT!
